<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">مِثَالُهُ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(ذَهَبَ التَّاجِرُ زَيْدٌ)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">فَالبَدَلُ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(زَيْدٌ)</span>، مَرْفُوعٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَيَقَعُ البَدَلُ:</span> لِشَيْءٍ مِنْ شَيْءٍ، أَوْ لِبَعْضٍ مِنْ كُلٍّ، أَوْ لِاشْتِمَالٍ، أَوْ لِتصْحِيحِ غَلَطٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">فَمِثَالُ الأَوَّلِ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(جَاءَ الأُسْتَاذُ زَيْدٌ)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَمِثَالُ الثَّانِي:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(قَرَأْتُ الكِتَابَ نِصْفَهُ)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَمِثَالُ الثَّالِثِ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(يُعْجِبُنِي زَيْدٌ عَقْلُهُ)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَمِثَالُ الرَّابِعِ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(جَاءَ زَيْدٌ خَالِدٌ)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>العَطْفُ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَحُرُوفُ العَطْفِ:</span> هِيَ حُرُوفٌ تُغْنِي عَنْ إِعَادَةِ الكَلَامِ المُكَرَّرِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَهِيَ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(الوَاوُ)</span>، وَ <span style="color:#008000">(الفَاءُ)</span>، وَ <span style="color:#008000">(ثُمَّ)</span>، وَ <span style="color:#008000">(أَوْ)</span>، وَ <span style="color:#008000">(أَمْ)</span>، وَ <span style="color:#008000">(إِمَّا)</span>، وَ <span style="color:#008000">(بَلْ)</span>، وَ <span style="color:#008000">(لَا)</span>، وَ <span style="color:#008000">(لَكِنْ)</span>، وَ <span style="color:#008000">(حَتَّى)</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَالمَعْطُوفُ - أَوِ العَطْفُ -: هُوَ التَّابِعُ الَّذِي يَكُونُ بَعْدَ حَرْفِ العَطْفِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَهُوَ:</span> يَتْبَعُ مَتْبُوعَهُ فِي الإِعْرَابِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span style="color:#006d98">مِثَالُهُ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(جَاءَ زَيْدٌ وَخَالِدٌ)</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span style="color:#006d98">فَحَرْفُ العَطْفِ:</span> الوَاوُ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالمَعْطُوفُ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(خَالِدٌ)</span>، مَرْفُوعٌ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>الحَالُ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالحَالُ:</span> اسْمٌ يُذْكَرُ لِوَصْفِ حَالِ صَاحِبِهِ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَيُعْرَفُ بِأَنَّهُ:</span> جَوَابُ <span style="color:#008000">(كَيْفَ)</span>.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَهُوَ:</span> مَنْصُوبٌ.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَلَا يَكُونُ إِلَّا:</span> نَكِرَةً، وَفَضْلَةً <span style="color:#008000">(أَيْ لَيْسَ مِنْ تَمَامِ الكَلَامِ)</span>.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span style="color:#006d98">مِثَالُهُ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(جَاءَ زَيْدٌ رَاكِبًا)</span>.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span style="color:#006d98">فَالحَالُ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(رَاكِبًا)</span>.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>